MACON COUNTY: Satulah Mountain: Down the blue trail
on Satulah Mountain. Elev. 1375 m. Co-occurring species
include witch hazels (spp. unknown), *Kalmia latifolia*, and
*Vaccinium* spp. Flowers in bud. Mix of old and new leaves.
Lat. 35.04007 Long. -83.19361 Datum: WGS84
